<subSubSection id="E8120BDEC416B8C97A0E354BE2363C5C" pageId="18" pageNumber="37" type="holotype">
<paragraph id="71FC2593C2FC3E027AB5A0B260006132" pageId="18" pageNumber="37">Holotype.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="7E9F173AE84FA0BE3CB20B9D5599C4CE" pageId="18" pageNumber="37">
Male (USNM), glued on pinned point, genitalia attached in microvial, labeled: printed &quot;Peru: Loreto, Cmp. S. Branch, 11 May 90 
<geoCoordinate id="19097000D36B97B45BF7B02937D87BBC" degrees="75" direction="west" minutes="20" orientation="longitude" precision="925" value="-75.333336">75°20'W</geoCoordinate>
, 
<geoCoordinate id="60A4B03D6C472611D7633C7DAF884331" degrees="05" direction="south" minutes="12" orientation="latitude" precision="925" value="-5.2">05°12'S</geoCoordinate>
